{
  "chapter": 4,
  "chapter_summary": "第四回「元宝·女人·狗」讲述富贵山庄因女人和金钱的到来而掀起波澜。王动、郭大路、燕七、林太平四人过着贫穷却快乐的日子，林太平刚被收留，正逐渐融入这个奇特的群体。郭大路打猎归来，带回一个猴子和一群自称走江湖卖艺的人——酸梅汤、飞豹子、小玲珑、小金刚。酸梅汤活泼大方，郭大路将后面五间屋子免费租给他们。次日一早，酸梅汤等人不告而别，留下五口箱子充作房租，箱中装满元宝和珠宝，价值足以买下整个富贵山庄。四人讨论这些财宝的来历，燕七指出酸梅汤一行人并非真正的卖艺者，财宝显然是偷来的。他们决定将财宝归还失主，来到山下麦老广的饭铺打听消息，却未听说有失窃案。此时三个神秘人物出现在饭铺：清河县捕头夹棍、北九省总捕头金狮，以及一个全身黑衣、背负乌鞘长剑的神秘剑客。原来城中确实有人被盗，一位妇人哭诉丢了三千两金子。夹棍等人正是为调查此案而来。黑衣人与金狮之间似乎有一种神秘的交易关系，在午时进行了一场金子交接。本章通过富贵山庄四人面对意外之财的选择，展现了他们重义轻利的品格，同时引入了新的悬念和危险人物。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我还没有死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里的确应该养只猫。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里本来有只猫，是燕七带回来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "猫呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "跟山下的公猫私奔了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人看来既不像疯子，也不像白痴，为什么偏偏有点疯病？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你那两个朋友呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "下山打猎去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "打猎？这种天气去打猎？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咕噜",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奇怪！今天怎么连老鼠的叫声都和平时不一样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是老鼠，是……是……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今天你运气总算不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我？运气不错？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今天我有种预感，他们打猎的收获一定不错，带回的东西说不定会让你大吃……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大吃一顿，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大吃一惊",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "吱吱",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你的朋友怕母猴子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "飞豹子",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁是小玲珑？谁是小金刚？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你猜猜看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小玲珑是你姐姐，对不对？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不对，她是我妹妹。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_suan_mei_tang",
      "speaker_name": "酸梅汤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来你好像有很多心事……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人本来就像个女孩子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就算男人全都没心没肺，至少都有肚子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_suan_mei_tang",
      "speaker_name": "酸梅汤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不说我倒差点忘了……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_jin_gang",
      "speaker_name": "小金刚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是你为什么从来也没有觉得不好意思呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_jin_gang",
      "speaker_name": "小金刚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "汪汪",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这地方已有十几年没这么热闹过了。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你放心，这里还有好几天热闹的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "几天？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "租金多少？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这房子究竟是你的？还是我的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你找什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "洗脸盆、洗脸布，还有漱口杯子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然洗，只不过是三日一小洗，五日一大洗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小洗是怎么洗？大洗是怎么洗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "燕七，你洗给他看看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我昨天刚洗过，今天该轮到你了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么你至少总该把洗脸的家伙拿过来吧。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "噗",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是小洗，是大洗。小洗若这么麻烦那还得了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你现在就磕吧，比我们脏的人满街都是。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么不索性脱下鞋子洗洗脚？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我正有这意思，只可惜时间来不及了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们一定也醒了，我到后面瞧瞧去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 323,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不是君子。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你好像一点也不喜欢那酸梅汤姑娘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 335,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看他们究竟是干什么的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 337,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们不是走江湖卖艺的么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 345,
      "line_end": 345
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁知道，也许是强盗都说不定。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 357,
      "line_end": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "听竹小院",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 377,
      "line_end": 377
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "听竹轩",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 377,
      "line_end": 377
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有竹无肉轩",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 379,
      "line_end": 379
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "听竹",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 379,
      "line_end": 379
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "听竹",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 381,
      "line_end": 381
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无肉",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 383,
      "line_end": 383
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你的客人已不告而别了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 393,
      "line_end": 393
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "走了就走了，这也用不着大呼小叫，大惊小怪的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 397,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "住房子本来就要付房租，这也没什么好稀奇的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 405,
      "line_end": 405
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "稀奇虽不稀奇，只不过付得太多了些。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 407,
      "line_end": 407
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "箱子里是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 409,
      "line_end": 409
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也没什么别的，只不过几箱铜臭物而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 411,
      "line_end": 411
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 427,
      "line_end": 427
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么箱子是哪里来的呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 429,
      "line_end": 429
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是抢来的，就是偷来的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 431,
      "line_end": 431
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些元宝后面的戳记都不同。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 433,
      "line_end": 433
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "能在一天晚上偷这么多人家，本事倒真不小。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 439,
      "line_end": 439
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这也不稀奇，高明的贼本就能日走千家，夜盗百户。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 441,
      "line_end": 441
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许他们是想栽赃。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 447,
      "line_end": 447
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "栽赃？为什么要栽赃？我们跟她又没有仇。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 449,
      "line_end": 449
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么办？人家既然送来了，我们当然就收下。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 459,
      "line_end": 459
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这事本来就简单得很'",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 465,
      "line_end": 465
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不简单。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 467,
      "line_end": 467
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有什么不简单？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 469,
      "line_end": 469
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "做贼也有学问，本来就不是人人都会做的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 491,
      "line_end": 491
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看我们最好将这些东西拿去还给别人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 493,
      "line_end": 493
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还给谁？谁知道这些东西是从谁家偷来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 495,
      "line_end": 495
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知道可以打听。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 497,
      "line_end": 497
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "到哪里去打听？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 499,
      "line_end": 499
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "麦老广",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 527,
      "line_end": 527
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "言茂源酒铺",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 531,
      "line_end": 531
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "娘舅家",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 549,
      "line_end": 549
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_lao_guang",
      "speaker_name": "麦老广",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "唔饮酒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 577,
      "line_end": 577
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然要，你先去拿十斤来，等等一齐算给你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 579,
      "line_end": 579
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这两天你可有听到什么消息没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 595,
      "line_end": 595
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许他们不是在这里偷的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 603,
      "line_end": 603
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一定是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 605,
      "line_end": 605
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是没有，而是不说，不敢说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 611,
      "line_end": 611
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "被偷又不是件丢人的事，为什么不敢说？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 613,
      "line_end": 613
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "随便。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 662,
      "line_end": 662
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是剑的杀气，是人的杀气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 674,
      "line_end": 674
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们知不知道这人是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 676,
      "line_end": 676
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "另外两个人我倒认得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 682,
      "line_end": 682
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们却不认得你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 684,
      "line_end": 684
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们很有名？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 690,
      "line_end": 690
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "棍子，倒也像，夹棍这名字就有点特别了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 696,
      "line_end": 696
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他也有这种本事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 702,
      "line_end": 702
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人的手段一定很辣。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 708,
      "line_end": 708
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他是干什么的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 718,
      "line_end": 718
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "清河县的捕头。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 720,
      "line_end": 720
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "清河县并不是个大地方，岂非埋没了人才？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 722,
      "line_end": 722
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那位金光闪闪的仁兄呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 730,
      "line_end": 730
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "凭良心讲，这人倒一点也不像狮子狗。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 736,
      "line_end": 736
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看过狮子狗没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 738,
      "line_end": 738
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各种狗我都看过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 740,
      "line_end": 740
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "狮子狗脸上什么东西最大？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 742,
      "line_end": 742
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "鼻子最大。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 744,
      "line_end": 744
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么东西最小？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 746,
      "line_end": 746
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嘴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 748,
      "line_end": 748
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我小时候养过好几条狮子狗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 750,
      "line_end": 750
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们再看看那人的脸。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 752,
      "line_end": 752
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "金毛狮子狗",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 754,
      "line_end": 754
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "果然是个特大号的鼻子。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 762,
      "line_end": 762
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他眼睛一定不太灵。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 764,
      "line_end": 764
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎么知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 766,
      "line_end": 766
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是到现在我还没有找到他的嘴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 774,
      "line_end": 774
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他的鼻子下面的那个洞，就是嘴了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 776,
      "line_end": 776
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那是嘴么，我还以为是鼻孔哩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 778,
      "line_end": 778
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "鼻孔上怎么会长胡子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 780,
      "line_end": 780
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我以为那是鼻毛。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 782,
      "line_end": 782
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人又是干什么的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 802,
      "line_end": 802
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看他穿得就像是个花花公子，实在不像是位名捕。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 808,
      "line_end": 808
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也不像穷光蛋。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 810,
      "line_end": 810
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他的本事又在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 812,
      "line_end": 812
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在鼻子上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 814,
      "line_end": 814
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "鼻子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 816,
      "line_end": 816
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这本事倒的确不小。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 822,
      "line_end": 822
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这两人可说全都是六扇门里一等一的顶尖高手，若不是什么大案子，绝惊动不了他们，所以……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 824,
      "line_end": 824
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你奇怪，他们为什么忽然到了这种地方来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 826,
      "line_end": 826
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 850,
      "line_end": 850
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_lao_guang",
      "speaker_name": "麦老广",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们姓什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 870,
      "line_end": 870
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_lao_guang",
      "speaker_name": "麦老广",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "男的姓高，女的娘家好像是姓罗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 872,
      "line_end": 872
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_lao_guang",
      "speaker_name": "麦老广",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刚过午时。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 880,
      "line_end": 880
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "拿来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 882,
      "line_end": 882
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_shi",
      "speaker_name": "金狮子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这地方不方便吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 884,
      "line_end": 884
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "方便。",
      "tone": "陈述",
